comment: Ca. 65 mL fresh ink (37 °C) at start. Layer override for layer 0: 20 s exposure, Z speed 30. Z hop height set to 3 mm. No pause. Print almost perfect, material overhang at bottom ("Saum", ca. 1 mm wide). Other than that, perfect. Rinsing print on printhead under running warm water. Detachment with metal spatula under running tap water. Fit check with metal implant replica: better fit than 211116 (V1) but not ideal yet.
next steps: Redesign ST implant V2 -> V3 and printing with same parameters.
